00:16:43.330 --> 00:16:45.710
Önce Super Saiyan...

00:16:51.880 --> 00:16:56.090
Bu, Super Saiyan'ı da,  
Super Saiyan 2'yi de aşan bir seviye...

00:16:59.100 --> 00:17:00.100
