00:19:40.260 --> 00:19:41.050
Evet!

00:19:41.260 --> 00:19:43.050
Goku-sa!

00:19:43.260 --> 00:19:44.680
Ay-ay-ay!

00:19:48.100 --> 00:19:54.860
